OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777637465
OL,3,CSouth East Water announces resignation
OL,4,Cof Independent Chair
OL,6,FSouth East Water has today announced
OL,7,Fthe resignation of Chair Chris Train.
OL,9,FIt follows a crossbench group of MPs
OL,10,Fsaid they have "no confidence" in
OL,11,FSouth East Water's (SEW) chief
OL,12,Fexecutive and board following the
OL,13,Fcompany's handling of major outages in
OL,14,FKent and Sussex.
OL,16,FBosses, including CEO David Hinton
OL,17,Fwere grilled twice by the MPs over
OL,18,Ftheir response to multiple supply
OL,19,Finterruptions across Kent and Sussex.
OL,26,@rD@POUrD@^O]
