OL,3,CSouth East Water announces resignation
OL,4,Cof Independent Chair
OL,6,FChris Train OBE became Chair of South
OL,7,FEast Water on 1 April 2022.
OL,9,FHe is also currently Non-Executive
OL,10,FChair of Clean Power Hydrogen and
OL,11,FChair of Sellafield Ltd.
