OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777637465
OL,3,CSouth East Water announces resignation
OL,4,Cof Independent Chair
OL,6,FLisa Clement, Interim Independent Non-
OL,7,FExecutive Chair, said: "The Board
OL,8,Fthanks Chris for his service to South
OL,9,FEast Water. The Company's focus
OL,10,Fremains on delivering engineering and
OL,11,Foperational changes that will
OL,12,Fstrengthen the resilience of South
OL,13,FEast Water's network and transform the
OL,14,FCompany for the benefit of customers
OL,15,Fand local communities."
OL,26,@oD@XOUwD@WO]
