PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777637465
OL,3,CSouth East Water announces resignation
OL,4,Cof Independent Chair
OL,6,FThe parliamentary Environment, Food
OL,7,Fand Rural Affairs (Efra) Committee
OL,8,Fsaid the leadership's incompetence and
OL,9,Flack of accountability have driven its
OL,10,Fpoor performance, while its inadequate
OL,11,Fgovernance framework has failed to
OL,12,Fhold senior employees responsible.
OL,14,FThousands of customers were left
OL,15,Funable to access tap water, shower or
OL,16,Fflush their toilets during the outages
OL,17,Fbetween November and January.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
