PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777637465
OL,3,CSouth East Water announces resignation
OL,4,Cof Independent Chair
OL,6,FIn a report, published on Friday, the
OL,7,Fcommittee said: "South East Water
OL,8,Fpresents as a company devoid of proper
OL,9,Fleadership, riddled with cultural
OL,10,Fproblems that raise serious concerns
OL,11,Fabout the ability of the executive
OL,12,Fteam, led by the CEO David Hinton, to
OL,13,Fbring the company back into compliance
OL,14,Fand deliver the services their
OL,15,Fcustomers deserve.
OL,17,F"Leadership teams play a major role in
OL,18,Fhow company culture develops; culture
OL,19,Fchange at this scale requires South
OL,20,FEast Water's leadership to change."
OL,26,@oD@QOUyD@AOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
