CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777637465
OL,3,CSouth East Water announces resignation
OL,4,Cof Independent Chair
OL,6,FThe report also called on SEW's
OL,7,Fshareholders ` Utilities Trust of
OL,8,FAustralia, NatWest Group Pension Fund,
OL,9,Fand Desjardins Group and associated
OL,10,Fholding companies ` to hold the
OL,11,Fcompany to account.
OL,13,FThe firm was fiercely criticised over
OL,14,Fmultiple failings that led to the
OL,15,Foutages as well as its response during
OL,16,Fthe crisis.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
