CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777637465
OL,3,CSouth East Water announces resignation
OL,4,Cof Independent Chair
OL,6,FThese included poor maintenance of
OL,7,Finfrastructure, failing to monitor
OL,8,Fcritical risks, failing to invest or
OL,9,Fbuild resilience and blaming external
OL,10,Ffactors such as climate change and
OL,11,Fincreased demand.
OL,13,FThe company was also accused of a
OL,14,Fdisorganised and slow response to
OL,15,Frestore supply, a lack of
OL,16,Fcommunication with customers and
OL,17,Finsufficient emergency supply through
OL,18,Fwater tankers and bottled water, which
OL,19,Fleft some vulnerable residents without.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
