PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777637465
OL,3,CSouth East Water announces resignation
OL,4,Cof Independent Chair
OL,6,FMr Hinton was grilled by the Efra
OL,7,Fcommittee in January but MPs said they
OL,8,Fhad concerns about the accuracy of his
OL,9,Fevidence and his lack of
OL,10,Faccountability.
OL,12,FThey then recalled the chief executive
OL,13,Falongside company chairman Chris Train
OL,14,Fto answer further questions at a
OL,15,Fhearing earlier this month.
OL,17,FIn a contrite appearance, Mr Hinton
OL,18,Fadmitted he "got it wrong" in his
OL,19,Fhandling of the outages and
OL,20,Facknowledged some of the team's
OL,21,Ffailings.
OL,26,@zD@MOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777637465
OL,3,CSouth East Water announces resignation
OL,4,Cof Independent Chair
OL,6,FBut in its report, the committee said
OL,7,Fthe leadership demonstrated a clear
OL,8,Fpattern of obfuscating responsibility
OL,9,Fand "groupthink", arguing that this is
OL,10,Fpreventing their ability to analyse
OL,11,Fproblems and learn lessons.
OL,13,FCommittee chairman Alistair Carmichael
OL,14,Fsaid the group of MPs "feel obliged to
OL,15,Fhighlight the gravity of this
OL,16,Fextraordinarily poor situation".
OL,18,F"This is an exceptional failure of
OL,19,Fmanagement and of corporate
OL,20,Fgovernance," he said.
OL,26,@qD@EOUqD@PO]vD@WOUxD@_O]zD@AOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
