PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777637465
OL,3,CSouth East Water announces resignation
OL,4,Cof Independent Chair
OL,6,F"One cannot overstate the dangers of
OL,7,Fso many communities losing water
OL,8,Fsupply for extended periods, including
OL,9,Fschools, GP surgeries and care homes.
OL,11,F"Someone in this company needs to take
OL,12,Fa grip, be accountable for its
OL,13,Ffailings and to put them right."
OL,15,FIn a holding statement, a spokesperson
OL,16,Ffor the water company said: "We are
OL,17,Fcarefully considering the details of
OL,18,Fthe Efra Committee Report, which is
OL,19,Fdue to be published tomorrow.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@`O]xD@]OU
